{"tid":136304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華160提名獲全數確認 成候選第一人","createTime":"2017-02-27T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T05:37:05.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd80ce4f1776ce06bcca60b3380751f06445400","tid":136304,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"曾俊華周六向選舉事務處遞交160個提名，成為第一人正式參選特首。據了解，選舉事務處已通知曾俊華競選辦，上周六提交的160個提名，全數獲確認，即曾俊華正式成為特首候選人。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華所遞交的提名，8成來自泛民，僅約35票來自建制，當中包括自由黨3票、酒店界選委兼合和實業董事總經理胡文新、詹培忠之子詹劍崙、亨達董事總經理徐聯安等。"},{"pid":"8cf7371c83713952c87575bfb9421bdd1e125c0b","tid":136304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50c34e8a38068c729532fca47ba35dee0508b57","tid":136304,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"葉劉入埋閘就好睇"},{"pid":"d0307cf8757294992b814b7b68ffcc78caeea015","tid":136304,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdc1a8256aa86b8b6c56494b183c6ee799cca8e","tid":136304,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"35票建制<br />\n<br />\n睇黎建制都有清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c455f08c77dc5a5ddcd88f42376fba71946573e5","tid":136304,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>35票建制<br />\n<br />\n睇黎建制都有清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n田大少話本來有 50 票"},{"pid":"1360bd479f486303a3cccae217360d876d1c3800","tid":136304,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"